OL,3,CWoman who underwent mesh surgery says
OL,4,Csurgeon should be banned
OL,6,FA woman who received a mesh operation
OL,7,Fthat may have been unnecessary from a
OL,8,FBristol surgeon has told ITV West
OL,9,FCountry he should "never be allowed to
OL,10,Fwork again".
OL,12,FAlison Buse, now aged 38, was only in
OL,13,Fher mid-twenties when she was referred
OL,14,Fto Antony Dixon at the Spire Hospital
OL,15,Fin Bristol.
OL,17,FShe's one of hundreds of people who
OL,18,Fclaim to have suffered painful side
OL,19,Feffects following a mesh operation
OL,20,Fcarried out by the surgeon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
