OL,3,CWoman who underwent mesh surgery says
OL,4,Csurgeon should be banned
OL,6,FMr Dixon worked at both Southmead and
OL,7,Fthe Spire Hospital where he carried
OL,8,Fout procedures such as rectopexy mesh
OL,9,Fand STARR, which involves using
OL,10,Fstaples, to treat rectal prolapse.
OL,12,FFollowing numerous complaints, North
OL,13,FBristol NHS Trust carried out a review
OL,14,Fand said more than 200 patients had
OL,15,Fbeen given unnecessary bowel
OL,16,Foperations by Mr Dixon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
