OL,3,CWoman who underwent mesh surgery says
OL,4,Csurgeon should be banned
OL,6,FThe mother-of-two was referred to The
OL,7,FSpire Hospital through private
OL,8,Fhealthcare, where she met Mr Dixon.
OL,10,FSpeaking of that first interaction she
OL,11,Fsaid: "He told me that I had a
OL,12,Fprolapse and that he could fix it for
OL,13,Fme. That he would do something called
OL,14,Fa rectopexy mesh and that would solve
OL,15,Fit.
OL,17,F"His words were 'please don't worry, I
OL,18,Fwill change your life and I will make
OL,19,Fyou feel better'.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
