OL,3,CWoman who underwent mesh surgery says
OL,4,Csurgeon should be banned
OL,6,F"He was adamant that this would help
OL,7,Fand this was the only surgery and
OL,8,Foption available."
OL,10,FThe Spire hospital previously found
OL,11,Fthat the operation may not have been
OL,12,Fnecessary and Mr Dixon's informed
OL,13,Fconsent process was inadequate, but
OL,14,Fthat the surgery was technically
OL,15,Fcompetent and there were no concerns
OL,16,Fwith the outcome of Ms Buse's
OL,17,Foperation, but she claims she has had
OL,18,Fnumerous operations as a result of his
OL,19,Fsurgery.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
