OL,3,CWoman who underwent mesh surgery says
OL,4,Csurgeon should be banned
OL,6,FFollowing the surgery Ms Buse said she
OL,7,Fstarted experiencing chronic pain.
OL,9,FShe added: "I wish I hadn't gone to
OL,10,Fsee him. I wish I hadn't trusted him.
OL,11,FI wish I'd questioned and asked more
OL,12,Fbut I think the way he explained, and
OL,13,Fwhat he told me about the surgery and
OL,14,Fthat it would be life changing, I
OL,15,Fthought that was it.
OL,17,F"I didn't think there was any other
OL,18,Foption and I thought I'd get better.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
