OL,6,F"I think he knew. When I think back
OL,7,Fover the conversation and the
OL,8,Finteraction, he was very pushy with
OL,9,Fthat operation.
OL,11,F"I think he should have his licence
OL,12,Ftaken off him forever. That's it.
OL,14,F"I have two young children. Having
OL,15,Fthose two children does make me carry
OL,16,Fon because, in all honesty, I have
OL,17,Fsaid to my mother, if I didn't have
OL,18,Fthem I would have given up.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
