OL,6,F"Despite my wrongdoing, my only wish
OL,7,Fwas to make (my patients) better. I
OL,8,Fconsidered that I was acting in my
OL,9,Fpatients' best interests, as the
OL,10,Ftribunal have accepted.
OL,12,F"I am very sorry and deeply regret the
OL,13,Fmisconduct described by the Tribunal
OL,14,F.... I am committed to learning from
OL,15,Fmy mistakes and to .. regain(ing)
OL,16,Fpeople's trust and to continue working
OL,17,Ftowards becoming once again the
OL,18,Fethical and trustworthy doctor that
OL,19,Fevery patient deserves and one that I
OL,20,Fwas previously recognised for.
